                <h3>Quick summary</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Best for Beginners:</strong> Vested Finance (zero commission, excellent research,
                        fractional shares, easy onboarding).</li>
                    <li><strong>Best for Simplicity:</strong> INDmoney (cleanest UI, integrated tax filing, zero
                        commission, good customer support).</li>
                    <li><strong>Best for Domestic Users:</strong> Groww (familiar interface for existing Groww users,
                        zero commission, limited features).</li>
                    <li><strong>Best for Traditional Investors:</strong> ICICI Direct Global (established bank, higher
                        fees, direct access to US brokers).</li>
                    <li><strong>Best for Advanced Traders:</strong> Interactive Brokers (lowest costs at scale,
                        professional tools, complex interface).</li>
                    <li>All platforms are <strong>LRS-compliant</strong> and allow investing up to $250,000 per
                        financial year.</li>
                </ul>
