            <div class="section-divider"></div> <!-- Section 8: How to Choose -->
            <section id="how-to-choose" class="article-section">
                <h2 class="section-title"><i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i> How to Choose the Right Platform</h2>
                <p>Your ideal platform depends on your investor profile. Here's a decision framework:</p>
                <div class="info-cards-grid">
                    <div class="info-card">
                        <div class="info-card-icon"> <i class="fas fa-graduation-cap"></i> </div>
                        <h4>For Beginners</h4>
                        <p><strong>Choose Vested</strong><br>Reason: Best research, fractional shares, easy onboarding,
                            and excellent educational content. You'll learn as you invest.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-card">
                        <div class="info-card-icon"> <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i> </div>
                        <h4>For Simplicity Lovers</h4>
                        <p><strong>Choose INDmoney</strong><br>Reason: Cleanest UI, integrated tax filing, and minimal
                            complexity. Just buy and hold.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-card">
                        <div class="info-card-icon"> <i class="fas fa-seedling"></i> </div>
                        <h4>For Existing Groww Users</h4>
                        <p><strong>Choose Groww</strong><br>Reason: Unified dashboard for Indian + US stocks. One app,
                            one login, one portfolio view.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-card">
                        <div class="info-card-icon"> <i class="fas fa-university"></i> </div>
                        <h4>For Traditional Investors</h4>
                        <p><strong>Choose ICICI Direct</strong><br>Reason: Bank-backed, relationship manager, physical
                            branches. Worth the high fees if you value trust and support.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-card">
                        <div class="info-card-icon"> <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i> </div>
                        <h4>For Advanced Traders</h4>
                        <p><strong>Choose Interactive Brokers</strong><br>Reason: Lowest costs at scale, professional
                            tools, options trading, global markets. Learn the complex interfaceâ€”it's worth it.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-card">
                        <div class="info-card-icon"> <i class="fas fa-wallet"></i> </div>
                        <h4>For Large Portfolios (>â‚¹10L)</h4>
                        <p><strong>Choose Interactive Brokers</strong><br>Reason: Currency conversion fees (0.08-0.2%)
                            beat everyone else. On â‚¹10 lakh, you save â‚¹5,000-8,000 vs fintech apps.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <h3 class="subsection-title">Decision Tree</h3>
                <div
                    style="background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3); padding: 30px; border-radius: 12px; margin: 30px 0; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); line-height: 2;">
